                     <interp inst="t18141026-71-verdict411" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               Of stealing, but not in the dwelling-house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18141026-71-punish412" type="punishmentDescription">
