                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18141026-71-defend705 t18141026-71-punish412"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
